# [OCM](../wg/ocm.html)

## Summary

The OCM Working Group held its first in-person meeting at IETF 126. The session featured updates on the core working group document `draft-ietf-ocm-open-cloud-mesh`, which recently moved to version -06. The group discussed several core aspects of the Open Cloud Mesh protocol, including IANA registries for extensibility, web app sharing and the OCM Integration Protocol (OCM-IP), structured notification updates, and federated groups using Message Layer Security (MLS). Implementers from FileSender and Nextcloud shared their status, requirements, and deployment experiences, followed by an open security and authentication discussion led by Aaron Parecki.

