### OpenCloudMesh State of the Art and Roadmap
* **Presenter:** Giuseppe Lo Presti
* **Slides:** [OpenCloudMesh state of the art and roadmap (OCM)](https://datatracker.ietf.org/meeting/126/materials/slides-126-ocm-opencloudmesh-state-of-the-art-and-roadmap-ocm-01)
* Giuseppe Lo Presti presented the history and trajectory of OCM, which aims to federate resource sharing across administrative domains without a common login.
* OCM is the foundation of the European Open Science Cloud (EOSC) federation, and complying with the OCM standard is now a tender requirement for the EU Node.
